{"tid":388570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發表文章\t發起投票\t回覆  八車撞埋鳩足咁亂 中環交通大受阻塞","createTime":"2017-09-05T14:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T14:20:17.000Z","uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef63b5806ecaaa6beff182b6cc0e08429cba797d","tid":388570,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T14:20:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">八車撞埋鳩足咁亂</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中環交通大受阻塞</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">小巴上一女乘客踫撞間受創</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/21366990_1815090565420639_785979139213526397_o.jpg?oh=82900d1a6e40e630e5aa00f202c1a474&amp;oe=5A2364CE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F21366990_1815090565420639_785979139213526397_o.jpg%3Foh%3D82900d1a6e40e630e5aa00f202c1a474%26oe%3D5A2364CE&h=c99a6702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n柏斯敦巴士台 plaxtonl's Bus Page shared 黎麗嫻's post.<br />\n1 hr &middot; <br />\n5/9 想當年，九巴N4行103期間，原來曾經出事。<br />\n#知您地淨係睇標題架喇<br />\n柏台講故：鳩足咁亂其實講乜呢？<br />\n大家首先要知鳩即係乜，其實就係一種雀鳥，同鴿一齊歸屬於Columbidae科。咁當成群鳩喺田野間覓食時，如果感覺有危險就會成群飛走哂而只留低腳印，通常啲腳印都亂過亂世佳人，分唔清邊隻打邊隻，所以就有鳩足咁亂嚟形容好混亂嘅情景喇！<br />\n#講吓㗎咋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/plaxtonlbuspage/posts/1427762187261478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplaxtonlbuspage%2Fposts%2F1427762187261478&d=03AktAJquTfWmOz0pf1dJgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f2f1406e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/plaxtonlbuspage/posts/1427762187261478</a></blockquote>"}]}